'''异抗坏血酸'''（{{lang-en|Erythorbic acid}}）是[[抗坏血酸|抗坏血酸]]（[[维生素C|维生素C]]）的[[立体异构体|立体异构体]]。<ref>[http://www.inchem.org/documents/jecfa/jecmono/v28je03.htm Erythorbic acid and its sodium salt] {{Wayback|url=http://www.inchem.org/documents/jecfa/jecmono/v28je03.htm |date=20220308013913 }} Dr R. Walker, Professor of Food Science, Department of Biochemistry, University of Surrey, England.</ref>它是由2-酮-<small>D</small>-葡萄糖酸甲酯和[[甲醇钠|甲醇钠]]反应而成的。它也可以从[[蔗糖|蔗糖]]或由[[青霉菌|青霉菌]]的菌株合成，这些菌株已被选择用于此功能。<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/Erythorbic_acid#section=Industry-Uses | title=Erythorbic acid | access-date=2021-10-15 | archive-date=2020-06-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610134955/https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/Erythorbic_acid#section=Industry-Uses }}</ref>它的[[E编码|E编码]]为E315，在加工食品中广泛用作[[抗氧化剂|抗氧化剂]]。<ref>[http://www.food.gov.uk/safereating/chemsafe/additivesbranch/enumberlist Current EU approved additives and their E Numbers] {{Wayback|url=http://www.food.gov.uk/safereating/chemsafe/additivesbranch/enumberlist |date=20101007124435 }}, Food Standards Agency</ref>

人们已经进行了临床试验来研究异抗坏血酸的营养价值。一项此类试验调查了异抗坏血酸对年轻女性维生素C代谢的影响，并未发现它对体内维生素C的吸收或清除有影响。<ref>{{cite journal | title = Effects of erythorbic acid on vitamin C metabolism in young women | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-clinical-nutrition_1996-09_64_3/page/336 | last = Sauberlich | first = HE |author2=Tamura T |author3=Craig CB |author4=Freeberg LE |author5=Liu T  | journal = American Journal of Clinical Nutrition |date=September 1996 | volume = 64 | issue = 3 | pages = 336–46 | doi = 10.1093/ajcn/64.3.336 | pmid = 8780343| doi-access = free }}</ref>后来的一项研究发现，异抗坏血酸是非血红素铁{{le|药物吸收|Absorption (pharmacology)|吸收}}的有效促进剂。<ref>{{cite journal | title = Erythorbic acid is a potent enhancer of nonheme-iron absorption | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-clinical-nutrition_2004-01_79_1/page/99 | last = Fidler | first = MC |author2=Davidsson L |author3=Zeder C |author4=Hurrell RF  | journal = American Journal of Clinical Nutrition |date=January 2004 | volume = 79 | issue = 1 | pmid = 14684404 | pages = 99–102 | doi=10.1093/ajcn/79.1.99| doi-access = free }}</ref>

异抗坏血酸用作腌肉和冷冻蔬菜的防腐剂。<ref>{{cite book | author = Hui YH | title = Handbook of Food Science, Technology and Engineering | publisher = CRC Press | year = 2006 | isbn = 0-8493-9848-7 | pages = 83–32 }}<!--page numbers don't make sense--></ref>

